    "body": "\"I have no idea where you got the idea that 1 GB cards are required for Win7, also pretty sure the playerbase would heavily disagree you there.\"\n\nThat's not what I meant by when I said that. Yes, it is not required, but what I meant was, in order to run Windows 7 - 10 without any slow downs or issues, you need to have at least a 1 gb card, atleast for the x64. I understand x86 is a little more lightweight so maybe users there can get away with only 512mb card.\n\nAnyways mailaender and chrisorbes made it clear they have no plans for right now, but maybe someday it will happen.\n"
